--- !u!114 &543929876
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 543929875}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 829b12bc487898c44ba9bed64d1ca9b3, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  kind: 1
  nextSceneName: Level_2
  loadSceneWhenFinished: 1
  onBeforeLoadScene:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  darkIntroSegments:
  - I have been waiting for you for longer than you remember.
  - ' You kept walking forward, but left pieces of yourself behind.'
  - In the rain you no longer ran. In the dark you no longer looked up.
  - I know all your frustration, your pain, your sadness, your silence, your doubt,
    your quiet despair.
  - And now I am here
  - "Not to blame you. Not to stop you. But to remind you\u2014"
  - "You are not broken. You are not lost. You are only\u2026 incomplete."
  - Come find me. Through the thorns. Through the silence. Through the self you buried
    away.
  - This time, do not turn back.
  - "Take my hand. And we will walk forward\u2014 together, into the light."
  introMessage: "Are you awake? \nYou seemed to have a long dream. \nwhere you have
    lost yourself\nwhere you have hated yourself\nRemember this photo?"
  photoSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bcb9e21f775b78044b1533bedeca8d53, type: 3}
  transitionParagraphs:
  - I thought I had only gone too far \nBut in the silent woods \n I lost even the
    way back
  - "Thorns at my feet \\nLight breaking on the ground \\nEach step\u2014  \\na memory
    slipping past"
  - Then I saw her
  - "In a forest full of sun she stood\u2014 \\nthe girl I once was"
  - Fearless \nMoving toward the light
  - She did not turn \nShe did not speak
  - But I understood
  - I had not lost the path  \nI had just lost the one who dared to follow it
  endPhotoSprite: {fileID: 0}
  chapterTitleText: Chapter2      Exploration
  chapterTitleFontSize: 128
  endCreditsSegments:
  - Thanks for your playing.
  - Get you get, and be confident
  darkenDuration: 1.2
  brightenDuration: 1.35
